{"id":171977,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/global-voices-叙利亚：斋戒月大屠杀，死亡人数攀升/","date":"2011-08-13T11:30:18Z","modified":"2011-08-13T11:30:18Z","title":"Global Voices | 叙利亚：斋戒月大屠杀，死亡人数攀升","content":"<p><p>叙利亚要求总统巴沙尔．阿萨德“离开”的呼声在斋戒月中持续着。随着死亡人数增加，阿拉伯世界的反应如潮水般涌来。</p>\n<p>叙利亚活跃人士上传影片并更新社群媒体平台，告知读者们当地最新发展。</p>\n<p><em>ShamSNN</em> 上传了一段<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2wJ5XV5HXjk\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2wJ5XV5HXjk\">影片</a>，影片中拉塔基亚做完泰拉威礼拜的群众高呼阿萨德下台。抗议活动是在斋戒日的晚上举行。</p>\n</p>\n<p><em>叙利亚愤怒之日</em>上传这段<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5w3UFW5vAUo\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5w3UFW5vAUo\">影片</a>，影片中是阿勒颇夜晚的抗议群众高呼人民要推翻政权：</p>\n</p>\n<p>多马的 <em>Abullahaldoumany</em> 这段<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wNHb7VldLKs\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wNHb7VldLKs\">影片</a>中据信是安全部队对抗议群众开火，也是发生在泰拉威礼拜之后：</p>\n</p>\n<p>叙利亚人 Leila Nachawati 在推特上说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/leila_na/status/100156612366442496\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/leila_na/status/100156612366442496\">@leila_na</a>：屠杀还在持续。政权宁可摧毁、残杀、烧毁整个国家，也不愿下台。#Syria #RamadanMassacre</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Razan Saffour 更新了今天的死亡人数统计：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/RazanSpeaks/status/100172819912073217\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/RazanSpeaks/status/100172819912073217\">@RazanSpeaks</a>：又是叙利亚血腥的一天。在荷姆和代尔泽尔有超过四十五人死于改革之名。#RamadanMassacre</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>阿拉伯联合酋长国的 Sultan Al Qassemi 引用阿拉伯人电视台的数据：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/SultanAlQassemi/status/100185696643465216\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/SultanAlQassemi/status/100185696643465216\">@SultanAlQassemi</a>：阿拉伯人电视台：今天有五十七名叙利亚活跃份子在军方行动中死亡。#RamadanMassacre #Syria</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>也门的 @NoonArabia 在推特上说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/NoonArabia/status/99808707122180096\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/NoonArabia/status/99808707122180096\">@NoonArabia</a>：真主保佑在前线为自由而战的利比亚人，以及叙利亚城市中面对恐惧和斋戒的叙利亚同胞。#Ramadan</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>在看到纪录叙利亚发生的暴行影片后，沙特阿拉伯博客 Ahmed Al Omran 在推特上说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/ahmed/status/99617780747350016\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/ahmed/status/99617780747350016\">@ahmed</a>：我周末有什么计划？看了今天叙利亚传出来的影片，我那些计划都不重要。#ramadanmassacre</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>同时，英国库德裔博客兼行动份子 Ruwayda Mustafah 问道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/RuwaydaMustafah/status/99483557893910528\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/RuwaydaMustafah/status/99483557893910528\">@RuwaydaMustafah</a>：阿拉伯联盟有考虑对叙利亚采取什么行动吗？还是这要求太高了？#RamadanMassacre</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>群众之声</em>也整理了一些影片和资讯，可以在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://crowdvoice.org/protests-in-syria\" href=\"http://crowdvoice.org/protests-in-syria\">这里</a>看到，注意有些影片相当血腥。</p>\n<p>请检视 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search?q=%23RamadanMassacre\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search?q=%23RamadanMassacre\">#RamadanMassacre</a> 标签以获得更多推特上关于斋戒月中叙利亚最新情势的讯息。</p>\n<p>更多注记 #RamadanMassacre 的影片可在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://twitter.com/#!/search/%23RamadanMassacre/grid/videos\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#%21/search/%23RamadanMassacre/grid/videos\">此处</a>看到。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/amira-al-hussaini/\" title=\"文章导读 Amira Al Hussaini\">Amira Al Hussaini</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/hllee/\" title=\"文章导读 Hsu-Lei Lee\">Hsu-Lei Lee</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/08/07/syria-death-toll-mounts-as-ramadan-massacre-continues/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/08/13/9661/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%8B%E6%88%92%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F13%2F9661%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F13%2F9661%2F&#038;desc=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%8B%E6%88%92%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F13%2F9661%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F13%2F9661%2F&#038;text=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%8B%E6%88%92%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F08%2F13%2F9661%2F&#038;title=%E5%8F%99%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%96%8B%E6%88%92%E6%9C%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%9D%80%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%E6%94%80%E5%8D%87\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%